fields.lyrics:
Ko-ko-ko-kosken-ko-ko-ko-korvaa,
siitä aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit saa.
Ko-ko-ko-kosken-ko-ko-ko-korvaa,
siitä aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit.
aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit,
aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit saa!

La-la-la-lappeen Ra-ra-ra-rantaan,
siellä aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit saa.
La-la-la-lappeen Ra-ra-ra-rantaan,
siellä aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit,
aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit,
aina kunnon rä-kä-kä-kännit saa!

We-we-we-Westendinrantaan,
siellä aina isin bemarissa saa.
We-we-we-Westendinrantaa,
siellä aina isin bemarissa,
aina isin bemarissa,
aina isin bemarissa saa!

Ta-ta-ta-Tammerkoskenrantaan,
siellä aina kunnon teini*krhm* saa.
Ta-ta-ta-Tammerkoskenrantaa,
siellä aina kunnon teini*krhm*,
aina kunnon teini*krhm*,
aina kunnon teini*krhm* saa!
fields.title: a

fields.lyrics:
:,: Minun juomani kossu on,
vaikk' on viljaviinaa. :,:
:,: Hei luulia illalla,
vaikk' on viljaviinaa. :,:

:,: Silmät siit saan punaiset,
sekä kieronlaiset. :,:
:,: Hei luulia illalla,
sekä kieronlaiset. :,:

:,: Mullon räkä poskella,
sekä turpa täynnä. :,:
:,: Hei luulia illalla,
sekä turpa täynnä. :,:

:,: Kun minä menen kapakkaan,
niin portsaritkin nauraa. ;.;
;.; Hei luulia hah hah haa,
portsaritkin nauraa. ;.;
fields.title: b

fields.lyrics:
Dear friends, the party may begin,
we raise our glasses to the man of the hour.
:,:We don't drink any light beers here,
only champagne can bring us joy.:,: 

We shall pour drinks down our throats,
and then remember the good, teekkari times
:,:As our drinking songs go on,
the party spirit is at its best:,:
fields.title: Hyvät ystävät - Dear Friends (1)

fields.lyrics:
Let us raise our glasses,
We have Koskenkorva
Let the beer turn flat,
A malt unworthy
:,: Riemuella permits him to,
So Veikko drinks :,:

Beer with its power
Excites us.
Along with Koskenkorva
Raises spirits
:,: It brings consolation,
So Veikko drinks :,:
fields.title: Nostakaamme malja – Let us raise our glasses (2)

fields.lyrics:
Here's the first
Sing "hopp faderallal lallall lei "
Here's the first
Sing "hopp faderallal lallall lei "
He who doesn't drink the first
Shall never, ever quench his thirst
Here's the fiiiiiiiiiiiiiirst
[Drink]
Sing "hopp faderallal lallall lei "
fields.title: Helan Går – First down (4)

fields.lyrics:
Koskenkorva
It will always get you smashed.
Koskenkorva
It will always get you smashed
always get you smashed
always get you smashed!

Lappeenranta
You'll always get smashed there.
Lappeenranta
You'll always get smashed there
always get smashed there
always get smashed there!
fields.title: Ko-ko-ko-koskenko-ko-ko-korvaa (6)

fields.lyrics:
Let's sing about water,
which we always have aplenty.
No matter how much you drink it,
it will never run out.
Little-Aqu's thirst is great
like Pauli's and Antero's.
AH, how great
Fresh water tastes

Aaaand water and water and water is so good
so very very cheap,
so healthy and so wet
1, 2, 3, - WATER!

What about in the morning
You are feeling great.
You carry buckets of water 
next to your bed.
Early-morning hours in the toilet,
You think, fingers down your throat:
AH, how great
Fresh water tastes

Aaaand water and water and water is so good
so very very cheap,
so healthy and so wet
1, 2, 3, 4
fields.title: Aqua vera (9)

fields.lyrics:
More booze into my glass,
More glasses onto this table,
More tables to this party,
More parties for people.
More people for Finland,
More Finland all over the land,
More land for Finland,
Let's march, let's march to Karjala, to Karlaja.
fields.title: Internationalen – International (11)

fields.lyrics:
The pope's life is wonderful,
he gets all the money people pay for pardons
:,:he drinks the most expensive drinks
- oh to be pope for a day. :,:

But, oh but, he can never taste
a young woman's lips
:,: He goes to sleep alone every night
- I wouldn't want to be a pope after all! :,:

But a sultan, he gets to party
and lives in a harem
:,: Amid beautiful women
- I'd gladly be a sultan :,:

But no, he's got his problems too
He's bound by the Koran's rules.
:,: He can't ever taste a drop of wine
- I wouldn't want to be a sultan after all! :,:

Alone I would want to be
Neither pope nor sultan.
:,: But I'd be happy to take turns
being sometimes one and sometimes the other :,:

Grant me a kiss, my lady
I'm a sultan for a while
:,:Hey, fellows, fill the cup
as I become pope once more :,:
fields.title: Paavi ja sulttaani – The Pope and the Sultan (13)

fields.lyrics:
They days of our lives so unsober
Have cast a fate hard on us all
:,:When yesterday I came home hell it was today,
Today I will arrive tomorrow:,: (TOMORROW)

Oh bloody hell, we’ll pass out, won’t get laid.
Brothers, sisters please rush, come to aid
We seize the bar man’s storage and won’t let it slip,
The vodka bottle’s empty with one sip. (WITH ONE SIP)
We seize the vodka bottle and won’t let it slip
The bar man’s storage’s empty with one sip.
(WITH ONE SIP)
fields.title: Elomme päivät epäselvät – The days of our lives (16)

fields.lyrics:
When you can drink water,
It might save you
You won't get smashed
You won't start a drinking spree.
Water is a treat,
it moistens the throat.
No need to drink alcohol,
No way to screw up.

You feel fresh,
Things won't get out of control.
In the morning
You won't have a hangover.
fields.title: Se kolmas vesilaulu – That third song about water (19)

fields.lyrics:
Who feels like paying,
who has money?
Who has lots of coins
that we can drink away?
fields.title: Wer Soll – Who must (20)

fields.lyrics:
I would take some Karhu vodka,
if I could only get some.
:,: I'd drink the whole bottle
and then throw up. :,:

Tiu-tau-tiu-tau-tili-tali-tittan,
let's drink rum with coke.
:,: When we have drank everything,
we'll be totally wasted. :,:

I don't think mother will take
any Karhu vodka,
:,: she doesn't even believe that
Karhu vodka is real. :,:

Tiu-tau-tiu-tau-tili-tali-tittan,
let's drink Koskenkorva with vichy.
:,: When we have drank everything,
we'll be totally wasted. :,:
fields.title: Karhu-viinaa - Karhu (”bear”) vodka (21)

fields.lyrics:
If your missus forbids you from drinking,
then drink, then drink
If she forbids you from bringing liquors,
then bring them, then bring them,
But don't you ever stop drinking,
just get yourself a better woman
And drink and sing, and drink and sing,
and drink and sing, and drink and sing...

(from German)
Drink, drink, brother drink
leave your worries at home
drink, drink, brother drink
empty your glass with me
Avoid the heartache, avoid the pain
Then life is good
To dear Augustin
Buy yourself a car and drive into a tree
That's when life is a dream.

Officers fight wars
and drink, and drink,
and taste spirits in tents,
and drink, and drink.
When battle goes on, the guns are blazing
And the officers take a swig,
and drink, and sing …

Teachers teach in the schools,
and drink, and drink,
and in the evening, end their lessons,
and drink, and drink.
During the day they teach German and math
then in the street in the evening they BELLOW AND THUNDER
and drink, and sing...
fields.title: Jos eukkosi kieltää sua juomasta – If your missus forbids you from drinking (25)

fields.lyrics:
Two journeymen traveled
Singing on the highway.
And in their song they brought out
A noble thought:
“If all the lakes in Finland
turned into liquor,
then wouldn't our lives
be worth living?” - Oh yes!

:,: Beer, beer,
Beer beer beer beer beer:,:

On the shore of Lake Liquor
we'd build a cottage
and on its sweet waves
we'd row night and day.
And we'd drink only liquor
In liquor we would swim
Oh couldn't you just
Compare this to Eden – Oh yes!

:,: Beer, beer,
Beer beer beer beer beer:,:

If a cure
To hangovers is never found
Then in the arms of Lake Liquor
We'd jump to go die
And we'd drink only liquor
In liquor we would swim
Oh couldn't you just
Compare this to Eden – Oh yes!

:,: Beer, beer,
Beer beer beer beer beer:,:
fields.title: Kaks' kisälliä – Two journeymen (26)

fields.lyrics:
In France they drink wine,
In Germany beer, in Russia vodka.
In Finland they drink everything,
So let's raise a glass to that.
fields.title: Eurovision (27)

fields.lyrics:
Don't you even dare suggest that we would drink
That hell-brought alcohol here,
No matter whose breath you would smell,
It would be fresh.

Hooray to us, the young water-boys
our heads are always clear
hangovers never near.
Hooray to us, the young water-boys,
and to our sober nature.

When you live meekly as we do,
Calmly by yourself,
Your nose stuck in your book.
We vigorously spit in our glass,
There is no greater joy.

Hooray to us...

Devil take those
That demonstrate their gluttony
When they get drunk.
Things like that will cause society's downfall
and bring culture to ruin.

Hooray to us...
fields.title: Vesipoikien marssi – The water-boys' march (29)

fields.lyrics:
I was once young and happy
I had money and a faithful wife
But I ended up in that skank's party
Now I hum and smoke tobacco


Tobacco, whisky and wild women
 they will ruin you, they will take your sanity
Tobacco, whisky and wild women
 they will ruin you, they will take your sanity

I'm a miserable and broken outcast, oh
you can see it in my face
Just this last story I'll tell,
what became of whisky and women

 Tobacco, whisky ...

For several years I drank whisky,
and in the bosoms of women I had joys.
But when I lit a cigarette,
my heart started pounding strangely.

 Tobacco, whisky ...

Thus write on my gravestone:
Because of whisky and women he rests here
Dear friends, take note
this happens to all who hum and drink.

 Tobacco, whisky ...
fields.title: Tupakka, viski ja willit naiset – Tobacco, whisky and wild women (30)

fields.lyrics:
My motherland is great and beautiful,
the land of forests, mountains, lakes.
:,: I know no other country,
as free as mine. :,:

From Moscow to our borders,
from the south to the north.
:,: The citizens are rulers
of their inmeasurable motherland. :,:

The level of culture is high,
the inventions prove that:
:,: there's a library in every kolkhoz
a few can already read. :,:

We have many universities,
many students in them.
:,: Studying is easy,
as long as you know if it's njet or da. :,:

We're rulers of the space,
a dead dog goes around the world.
:,: Technology is easy,
if only we could make the Moskvitch work. :,:

We breed cows,
we raise shrimps.
:,: Salmonella is always a problem,
but we'll defeat it with vodka. :,:

Communism is an almighty ideology,
it spreads across the world.
:,: We always appreciate freedom,
that's why we take it from the others. :,:
fields.title: Moskovalaisen ylioppilaan laulu - The song of a student from Moscow (31)

fields.lyrics:
An unbreakable union of free republics,
The Great Russia has welded forever to stand!
Long live the creation of the will of the people,
The united, mighty Soviet Union!

CHORUS: 
Be glorious, our free motherland, 
A reliable stronghold of peoples' friendship! 
The Party of Lenin, the strength of the people, 
Leads us to the triumph of Communism! 
Through tempests the sun of freedom shone to us,
And the great Lenin illuminated our path,
To a just cause he raised up the peoples,
To labour and heroic deeds he inspired us!

CHORUS 

In the victory of the immortal ideas of Communism
We see the future of our country,
And to the Red Banner of our glorious Motherland
We shall always be selflessly true!

CHORUS
fields.title: Neuvostoliiton hymni – National anthem of the Soviet Union (32)

fields.lyrics:
Uncle Lenin lives in Russia
It's a long way from there to Vietnam
But to me it feels like
Uncle Lenin lives as close
as uncle Ho Tshi Minh

Lenin has such a big forehead
that it can fit the whole Earth and heaven too
And uncle Lenin smiles
and his eyes twinkle and he laughs
like uncle Ho Tshi Minh

Uncle Lenin lives in Russia
I'll invite him to visit Vietnam
He loves us
He's just as sweet to us
as uncle Ho Tshi Minh

I'm just a little pioneer
My strength is still small
But a little one can fight too
For the peace like Lenin
and uncle Ho Tshi Minh
For the peace like Lenin
and uncle Ho Tshi Minh
fields.title: Lenin-setä – Uncle Lenin (33)

fields.lyrics:
:,: The cottage of Servi's Maija 
on a high hill, :,:
the lords go there on a horse, 
the lords go there on a horse,
the lords go there on a horse,
the common people have to walk,
the common people have to walk.

:,: Servi's Maija's kids were 
related to monkeys, :,:
they were in the trees and they were on the ground,
they were in the trees and they were on the ground,
they were in the trees and they were on the ground,
and they were innumerable,
and they were innuberable.

:,: Servi's Maija makes coffee 
in an old boot. :,:
She did have a pot,
she did have a pot,
she did have a pot,
but it was in a pawn shop,
but it was in a pawn shop.

:,: Hindu and bamboo and banana are 
southern fruits, :,:
and they can't be compared,
and they can't be compared,
and they can't be compared
to potato and herring,
to potato and herring.
fields.title: Servin Maijan mökki - The cottage of Servi's Maija (37)

fields.lyrics:
On an island of lake Saimaa, at a small cottage's steps
Cultist Miikkulainen is making a sacrifice,
But only a seal breaks the surface of the lake
Which is disappointing.
Under the waves it followed the call
Of a sermon so familiar.
The song tells of what happens when you are alone,
To which the seal can relate well.

Heads are no longer sacrificed to Cthulhu,
The world is modernized.
The man and the seal are both
Mustached relics

On an island of lake Saimaa, at a small cottage,
The cult of the Ancients didn't want to stay.
One cultist was left alone, like the seal,
And fate took its master away.
Only one hundred seals are left in the great lake Saimaa,
Soon there might not be a single one.
Mikkulainen is sharpening the sacrificial knife.
A terrible thought in his mind


Heads are no longer ...

On island of lake Saimaa, at a small cottage
cultist Miikkulainen is screaming his spells.
On the sacrificial rock, a lifeless seal
Is already getting cold.
From below the waves of great Saimaa,
An ancient tentacled horror rises
An so, Miikkulainen's fate is just as the seal's
to be the last of their line.

Finally heads are sacrificed to Cthulhu,
The Ancient has returned to the world.
The man and seal are now both
Fools eaten for lunch
fields.title: Muinaisten valssi – Waltz of the Ancients (44)

fields.lyrics:
As the winter evenings get darker,
we come to the refuge of Poli (polytechnic) again,
:,:Our technology left us behind,
we want to forget that.:,:

Our master thesis is a dream,
every exam has expired,
:,:our old, unused compass sits rusted,
our ink has hardened in its bottle.:,:

Always we watch new teekkari generations
pass by our table,
:,:But we no longer have the strength
to join their ranks.:,:

The wine in our glasses mocks us,
inviting with its froth.
:,:Our troubles will disappear,
get wasted no matter the cost.:,:

(standing up)
And when Integer vitae
is sung to us for the last time.
:,:A beer barrel will be raised
To the grave of the eternal Teekkari.:,:
fields.title: Ikuisen teekkarin laulu – Song of the eternal teekkari (46)

fields.lyrics:
I wanna be the very best
Like no one ever was
To catch them is my real test
To train them is my cause

I will travel across the land
Searching far and wide
Teach Pokémon to understand[1]
The power that's inside

Pokémon (Gotta catch 'em all), it's you and me
I know it's my destiny
(Pokémon!)
ooh, you're my best friend
In a world we must defend
Pokémon (Gotta catch 'em all), a heart so true
Our courage will pull us through
You teach me, and I'll teach you
Po-ké-mon
(Gotta catch 'em all!)
Gotta catch 'em all!
Pokémon!
fields.title: Kaikki kerätään - Pokemon theme (22)
